This licence shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the place where the creator of the Hardware resides, provided that all disputes arising out of or relating to this licence shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of that place, unless otherwise agreed to in writing by both parties, in which case the disputes shall be resolved in accordance with the procedures set forth in Section 5.3.
